<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Mon Portfolio</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            transition: background 0.6s ease, color 0.6s ease;
        }

       
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #ff4b4b 0, #5a0000 35%, #050505 80%);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: background 0.8s ease, filter 0.8s ease;
        }

        
        .hero::before,
        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 70vmax;
            height: 70vmax;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.55), transparent 60%);
            filter: blur(40px);
            opacity: 0.8;
            z-index: 0;
            animation: float 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        .hero::before {
            top: -20vmax;
            left: -10vmax;
        }

        .hero::after {
            bottom: -25vmax;
            right: -15vmax;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(120, 0, 0, 0.8), transparent 60%);
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            100% { transform: translate(40px, -40px) scale(1.1); }
        }

        
        .nav {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 1.5rem 4vw;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        }

        .nav a {
            color: #f8f8f8;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .nav a:hover {
            color: #ffdedf;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* ----- BOUTON THEME ANIMÉ ----- */
        #theme-toggle {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        #theme-toggle:hover {
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
        }

        #theme-toggle::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            transform: rotate(45deg) translate(-100%, -100%);
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
        }

        #theme-toggle:hover::after {
            transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0%, 0%);
        }

        #theme-toggle:active {
            transform: scale(0.95) rotate(3deg);
        }

       
        .hero-center {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .hero-inner {
            max-width: 700px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .hero-kicker {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #ffb3b3;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #ffe5e5;
        }

        
        body.light-theme {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
        }

        body.light-theme .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #f0f0f0, #ffffff);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        body.light-theme .nav a,
        body.light-theme #theme-toggle {
            color: #000000;
            border-color: #000000;
        }

        body.light-theme .hero-title,
        body.light-theme .hero-subtitle {
            color: #222222;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .nav {
                justify-content: center;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 1rem;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="hero">

        
        <nav class="nav">
           <a href="{{ path('pourensavoirplus') }}" class="btn primary">
    Pour en savoir plus
</a>

         
            <button id="theme-toggle">Changer le théme</button>
        </nav>

        <div class="hero-center">
            <div class="hero-inner">
                <div class="hero-kicker">MY PORTFOLIO</div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">Fatou Binetou Diallo Groupe A2</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    Étudiante en 1ʳᵉ année de BUT Réseaux & Télécoms, j’explore les coulisses du numérique en apprenant à connecter, sécuriser et faire dialoguer les technologies qui façonnent notre monde.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer>
    <p>© 2025 Fatou Binetou Diallo — BUT Réseaux & Télécommunications</p>
</footer>


    </section>


    <script>
        const toggleBtn = document.getElementById("theme-toggle");

        
        const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem("theme");
        if (savedTheme === "light") {
            document.body.classList.add("light-theme");
        }

      
        toggleBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
            document.body.classList.toggle("light-theme");

            if (document.body.classList.contains("light-theme")) {
                localStorage.setItem("theme", "light");
            } else {
                localStorage.setItem("theme", "dark");
            }
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
